remarks.para:
If true, I-Load adds the following CSS declaration to the HTML code of the Image Upload/Edit Window:
            body 
            {
               direction: rtl;
               unicode-bidi: embed;
               text-align: right;
            }

If true, I-Load adds the following CSS declaration to the HTML code of the Preview Window:
            body 
            {
               direction: rtl;
               unicode-bidi: embed;
               text-align: right;
            }
